	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64527943">that I would actually be inclined to trust MS a bit on this one. In this specific regard, they're quite similar to Apple.
<br> <br>
Like Apple, Microsoft makes it's $$$$ selling software, hardware, and services. They don't make money selling ads and user data. Quite the opposite. MS is strongly incentivized to keep user data fairly secure. If they don't, they'll lose customers.
<br> <br>
Facebook, Google, and those other companies will extract every possible penny from my user data because, um, that's literally their business model.</div>
